  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p>Inghams have teamed up with award winning Airport Parking &amp; Hotels (APH) providing exclusive deals and the best prices for all your airport parking, hotels &amp; lounges needs. Get an instant quote and book online, saving up to 45% at participating car parks located at selected airports throughout the UK.</p>
<p>Parking your car at the airport couldn’t be easier with APH’s ‘Meet &amp; Greet’ where an APH chauffeur will meet you upon arrival at the airport, take your car to their industry recognised ‘Park Mark’ secure car park and delivering it back to you at the airport terminal when you arrive back from your holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: left; font-size: 24px; color: #023761; font-weight: bold; font-style: bold;">Book discounted Airport Parking, Hotels &amp; Lounges online</p>
<p><a name="parking"></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left; font-size: 18px; color: #023761; font-weight: bold; font-style: bold;">Save up to 35% on Airport Parking &amp; Hotels with APH</p>
<ul>
<li>Pre-book with APH and save up to 35% on standard airport parking rates – Plus receive an additional 20% discount off participating car parks at all major UK airports.<br /><br /></li>
<li>APH ‘Meet &amp; Greet’ valet parking – ideal for transporting bulky luggage and ski equipment.  No transfer buses, just drive straight to the airport.<br /><br /></li>
<li>Exclusive APH Airport Hotel &amp; Parking package deals.<br /><br /></li>
<li>Safe and secure parking delivered by APH - multiple winner of Best Airport Parking Company at the British Travel Awards.<br /><br /></li>
<li><strong><a rel="noopener" href="https://partners.aph.com/ing" target="_blank">Click here</a> and book your Airport Parking &amp; Hotels</strong></li>
</ul>
<p>If you prefer to make your booking by phone please call the APH team on <strong>0800 014 7102 / 01342 859 600</strong> and quote <strong>"</strong><strong>ING"</strong> to get the <strong>best prices</strong> available.</p>
<p><strong><br /></strong> Inghams in partnership with Airport Parking &amp; Hotels offer the <strong>best deals and exclusive rates</strong> for all your Airport Parking, Hotels and Lounges needs – <strong><a rel="noopener" href="https://partners.aph.com/ing" target="_blank">click here and book online today</a></strong>.</p>
<p><em>Please note that we act at all times as selling agent for the supplier in respect of all "APH" services. See our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a> for full details.</em></p>
<p> </p>
<h2><strong><a name="bloc"></a>Special offer at Gatwick Bloc Hotel - book a double room at a 'special rate'!</strong></h2>
<p>If you have got an early flight from Gatwick or simply want a hassle free start to your holiday. We are pleased to offer our Inghams guests, a special rate at the <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="http://www.blochotels.com/gatwick/" target="_blank">Gatwick Bloc Hotel</a>, which is situated right inside the South Terminal building. We have negotiated a <strong>special</strong> <strong>rate</strong> on top of your Inghams holiday price, you can book a double room with window at this new hotel. Step straight from reception into the departures area!</p>
<p><strong>How to Book</strong></p>
<p>To take advantage of this offer, please book your double room directly with the hotel on <strong>0203 051 0101</strong> or e-mail: <a href="mailto:bookingslgw@blochotels.com">bookingslgw@blochotels.com</a>, quoting code <strong>INGBLGW</strong> and your <em><strong>Inghams Booking Reference</strong></em>. Payment per person is to be made in full to hotel at time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<p>Offer is subject to availability and can be withdrawn at any time. Rooms based on 2 adults sharing. Single supplement will incur an additional charge per room. Bloc Hotel will verify the bookings with Inghams to ensure the conditions are met.</p>
<p>Why not take a look at our <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/908541927e0e430a95d53f92491941c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/908541927e0e430a95d53f92491941c2}" title="Gatwick Ski Deals">latest ski deals departing from Gatwick Airport &gt;</a> </strong>or take a look at our <strong><a data-udi="umb://document/45df95da573f4e34a157981d6ff91671" href="/{localLink:umb://document/45df95da573f4e34a157981d6ff91671}" title="Gatwick Late Deals">latest summer deals departing from Gatwick Airport &gt;</a></strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p><em>Please note that we act at all times as selling agent for the supplier in respect of all third party services. See our <a data-udi="umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b703ff07ccec43baad41fffcfcc61821}" title="Terms &amp; Conditions">terms and conditions</a> for full details.</em></p>]]></bodyText>
